name: Barry Mark
description: Amazing taste, hot and fresh food , reasonable prices and quick service, very impressive food

name: Cheery Berry
description: The Food on call service is good, innovative and fast. Food taste is also good.But the food is little bit spicy and oily.Need to improve a little.

name: Tom Mark
description: I  received a delicious food package from Foodu a couple of days back for testing and review. It was all homemade food and by the chefs who dropped a little note with every food item.Foodieare very professional and there is like magic in chef's hands that you can’t stop craving for their delicious food.
